Class TrafficLightProgramPhase

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.eclipse.mosaic.lib.objects.trafficlight.TrafficLightProgramPhase

    Serializable
    public class TrafficLightProgramPhase
extends Object
implements Serializable
    This class represents a traffic light phase within a traffic light program, characterized by its duration and certain states of traffic lights.
